nodes.text: Three seven nine aitch oh ell forty-four underscore bee nine two one

Three seven nine aitch oh ell forty-four underscore bee nine two one (379HOL44_B921)was a high-level, extremely classified access code reserved for use by the upper echelons of the Galactic Alliance Guard. At the bottom of the unassigned list, three seven nine aitch oh ell forty-four underscore bee nine two one had been all but forgotten about by GAG personnel until it was secretly stolen and used to infiltrate the Galactic Alliance Defense Force's systems by Lumiya, Dark Lady of the Sith.
